/*
  # Add Full Granular Product Catalog from Supplier PDF

  ## Overview
  Full item-by-item extraction of the uploaded supplier catalog ("E catalog _compressed.pdf"),
  going beyond the earlier consolidated migration (20260705000000). The catalog contains
  ~330 individually photographed items across 16 pages; this migration adds every one of
  them that is not already represented in the `products` table (86 original + 29 from the
  prior consolidated migration), including distinct size/model/color variants and the
  cutlery/flatware pattern codes from the smallwares section.

  Each row is guarded by a NOT EXISTS check on product name, so this migration is safe to
  run more than once and after the prior consolidated migration.

  ## Placeholder images
  As before, no per-item photography was available, so rows reuse existing generic
  equipment photos from /public as stand-ins pending real product photos via Admin > Products.

  ## Notes on source data
  Descriptions and features were generated directly from the spec lines printed under each
  photo in the catalog (model, size, power, voltage, capacity). Where the same catalog name
  covered multiple size/power/color variants, the distinguishing spec was appended in
  parentheses to keep names unique (e.g. "Washing Machine (Capacity: 20kg)").
*/

